        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19173926/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19173926/" class="">第16页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/9105179/" class=" " title="Sangha">Sangha</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19173926">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">每当我似乎感受到世界的深刻意义时，正是他的简单使我震惊</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-06-23 21:55</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">4人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>每当我似乎感受到世界的深刻意义时，正是他的简单使我震惊</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
